    "Phase 4 #474 — pinned versions + SHA-256s of every JS/WASM bundle",
    "served by synth-cdn at /lib/* (ClusterIP only — UI nginx reverse-proxies",
    "from /api/cdn/lib/* same-origin path; nothing outside the cluster touches this svc)",
    "",
    "build-libs.sh fetches each entry, verifies sha256, and bakes into the",
    "synth-cdn image. CI verifies SHAs on every build — mismatch fails the",
    "build, preventing supply-chain swaps mid-conversation.",
    "",
    "Bumping a version: replace the version + sha256 fields, run",
    "  cd services/synth-cdn && ./build-libs.sh --verify-only",
    "to fetch + diff before committing."
  ],
